<HEADLINE>
<P>
WALK LIKE A MAN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
We instructors in the aerobics profession have been trying very hard to entice 
men into the aerobics room. It is a great workout for anyone, any age, any sex. 
It is not a woman's domain. Men are already hesitant to try for fear of being 
confronted by women like Littwin. I hope none of my class members read her 
article, or I'll have to start back at square one! One more man in aerobics 
equals one less couch potato! 
</P>
<P>
JUNE SCHNEIDER 
</P>
<P>
Redondo Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
