<P>
Photo, Tom and Pam Korman, trustees of Wolfgang Puck Charitable Foundation, 
chaired cocktail reception at Bullocks Wilshire. Over $250,000 was raised last 
year for Meals on Wheels. SILVIA MAUTNER 
