<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE NEIGHBORHOOD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The article "Living Downtown" (by Myrna Oliver, March 22) really caught my 
attention. But I am angry that the term Latinos was used in such a way as to 
classify them as "undesirables" for the upper-middle and upper classes to 
interact with. I'm offended, and I believe an apology to the many Latinos whom 
you have offended is in order. 
</P>
<P>
And don't be too surprised if some of those residents of that beautiful 
skyscraper land are Latinos. 
</P>
<P>
VALERIE RAYAS 
</P>
<P>
Gardena 
</P>
