<P>
Word that she would receive several hundred thousand dollars in compensation 
for the May, 1987, death of her son in the missile attack on the guided missile 
frigate Stark in the Persian Gulf made Pat Stevens of Visalia cry for sorrow 
and say she would "rather be a bag lady and have Jimmy back." The money is 
