SALVADOR -- ARMED FORCES; HAMMER, MICHAEL P; JIMENEZ MORENO, JOSE ALFREDO; 
LLOVERA BALLETE, ORLANDO; LOPEZ SIBRIAN, RODOLFO; PEARLMAN, MARK DAVID 
</P>
