ASSOCIATION; LOS ANGELES FIRE DEPARTMENT; RACKETEERING; SLUMS; APARTMENTS -- 
LOS ANGELES; T H I S CORP; SUITS; LANDLORDS; RENTAL HOUSING; KARMELICH, BEN; 
CASTANEDA, DAVID 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
