<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE TIMES' ALL-INLAND BASKETBALL TEAM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Times' all-star basketball awards banquet is today at the Anaheim Hilton 
Hotel. Male and female athletes from 14 zones will be presented awards, with a 
coach and player of the year being named from each region. 
</P>
<P>
</P>
