54 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
GOOD TIME TO PLANT JAPANESE MAPLE TREE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Now is a good time to plant a Japanese maple tree -- it fits into any garden. 
It grows as a small tree or shrub that offers spring growth in a red color, 
soft green summer leaves and fall foliage of scarlet, orange or yellow. As a 
bonus, it provides a graceful silhouette of delicate green or red branches in 
the winter. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA040289-0197 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 39032 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 2, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
