<P>
Photo, Richard C. White ; Photo, Christa S. Scarpelli ; Photo, Larry Smith ; 
Photo, Larry Freeberg ; Photo, Mark McLaughlin ; Photo, Thomas W. Davis 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
