<P>
WANG SIGNS LEASE FOR SANTA ANA OFFICE SPACE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WANG Laboratories of Lowell, Mass., has signed a five-year, $2.8-million lease 
for 32,800 square feet of office space at 4 Hutton Centre Drive, Santa Ana, the 
recently completed 203,144-square-foot office tower at Santa Ana's Hutton 
Centre complex. 
</P>
<P>
A worldwide supplier of computer-based information processing systems, WANG 
will establish its Sierra District office at Hutton Centre. It is a $35-million 
business unit servicing Orange, San Bernardino, Riverside, Imperial and San 
Diego counties. 
</P>
