<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMMERCIAL SCENE; 
</P>
<P>
WEBER SERVICES LEASES IN DISTRIBUTION CENTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Weber Distribution Services has signed a five-year, $4,888,000-lease for 
183,490 square feet of space in Miramar Distribution Center at 7825 and 7835 
Trade St. in the Miramar district of San Diego. 
</P>
<P>
The San Diego office of Grubb &amp; Ellis represented Weber, while the Rancho 
Bernardo office of Coldwell Banker represented the lessor, Miramar Distribution 
Center. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
